{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c384f3e7fa","title":"中共中央批转北京市委重要通告","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3e76d0ecde","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":20,"articleId":"c384f3e7fa"}],"tags":[{"id":"3bff1d2fc6","name":"暴力和武斗","type":"主题"},{"id":"46426acff1","name":"中共中央转发","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"53b954d860","name":"公安与法律","type":"主题"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33f2caef46","type":"title","text":"中共中央批转北京市委重要通告","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"f27cbe5444","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，各省、市、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"ed403bd761","type":"paragraph","text":"北京市委十一月十八日的重要通告，很好。现在转发全国，请各省、市、自治区用各省、市、自治区党委名义大量印发，在学校、厂矿、机关或其他单位内张贴。各地如有同样的情况，照这个通告办理。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"82f3faf169","type":"paragraph","text":"中  央","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"548db9b477","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十一月二十日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"2a486cf482","type":"paragraph","text":"重  要  通  告","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"f506cc3f2d","type":"paragraph","text":"任何厂矿、学校、机关或其他单位，都不许私设拘留所、私设公堂、私自抓人拷打。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"e9dba0be9d","type":"paragraph","text":"这样做是违犯国家的法律和党的纪律。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"1d3d23ddb6","type":"paragraph","text":"如果有人在幕前或者幕后指挥这样做，必须受到国法和党纪的严厉处分。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"6fbadf9db8","type":"paragraph","text":"从今天起，如有再犯以上罪行的，要立即处理。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"0a61b52936","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党北京市委员会","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"},{"id":"70f5fb3d2c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十一月十八日","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa"}],"page":{"id":"202e6c37d2","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c384f3e7fa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}